																								<li class="cat-post-item">
									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/tip-sheets/reporting/patient-zero-party-coronavirus/" rel="bookmark" title="The problem with using ‘patient zero’ and ‘party zero’ in coronavirus news">
